Interface CorpRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<Corp,String>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<Corp,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<Corp,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<Corp,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<Corp,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<Corp>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<Corp,String>
public interface CorpRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<Corp,String>
Repository interface for Corp entity.

This interface extends JpaRepository to provide CRUD operations for Corp entities. Additionally, it declares custom query methods to retrieve and update data based on specific conditions.

Each method is documented with its purpose and usage details.
